    "title": " 京东规则动态一览（2025年7月14日-2025年7月18日）",
    "followRuleId": "1262232615906316288",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1261956238145622016&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台机电散热类目招商激励政策（2025.7.1&mdash;&mdash;2025.9.30）》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">针对电脑、办公-电脑组件-机电散热类目下有效销售额达标的新店，返还一定比例的运营支持服务费。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1262238805629472768&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①全文规则表述简化，详细内容通过细则对规则进行补充说明；②部分违禁场景表述调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1260923001621319680\">《京东开放平台月饼商品管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确月饼商品的质量标准、抽检机制、售后和违规处理规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台类目资费规则》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">首档保证金阈值从0~3万调整为0~5万元。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259478084453797888\">《京东开放平台经营类目商品阈值明细表》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①2个类目新增设置阈值：生鲜-蛋类、生活日用-日用个护工具；②3个类目阈值变更：医疗保健-药食同源、传统滋补-养生茶饮、传统滋补-滋补营养品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259479258473041920\">《京东开放平台个人/个体经营类目商品阈值明细表》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259802974834790400\">《京东好营养-多种维生素多种矿物质片品质认证质量标准》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修改技术要求中的功能要求及功效成分指标要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259439390715940864&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台服务延迟报备规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">将4种报备类型增加至6种，新增定制商品相关的报备标准，支持商家对收货地址异常的报备。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259859855611662336\">《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①价格违规管理增加提价套取补贴场景及定义；②价格违规管理增加加收保证金、商品详情页屏蔽、限制区域销售、限制商品上架/发布、钱包冻结、类目/品牌停用等处置措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259859855611662336\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259334890139291648&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台一物一检合规管理规则》</a></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整商品质量不合格重度瑕疵及中度瑕疵的标准定义。</span></p>",
